OL,5,G0205 Gypsy Rose: Life After Lock Up
OL,6,     FKen issues Gypsy an ultimatum when
OL,7,     Fhe learns that she's planning to
OL,8,     Fmeet Ryan - with baby Aurora in
OL,9,     Ftow. With her family dynamic in
OL,10,     Fjeopardy, Gypsy's got a choice to
OL,11,     Fmake.
OL,12,G0300 Emergency Helicopter Medics
OL,13,     FThe heli-medics help a teen
OL,14,     Fmotorcyclist who's been hit by a
OL,15,     Fcar and catapulted into the air. A
OL,16,     Fholiday fitness workout ends in
OL,17,     FCPR. And a lorry driver is trapped
OL,18,     Fin his cabin.
